================================================================================
               ROVER WIRING SCHEMATIC (ARDUINO + L293D SHIELD)
================================================================================

[ POWER SOURCE ]
----------------
Battery (7.4V - 11.1V Li-ion) (+) ---> L293D Shield EXT_PWR (+)
Battery (7.4V - 11.1V Li-ion) (-) ---> L293D Shield EXT_PWR (-) / GND
* Note: Keep the PWR jumper ON if powering Arduino via Shield.

[ MOTORS (L293D Shield Terminals) ]
-----------------------------------
Motor Front-Right (FR) ---------> Terminal M1
Motor Front-Left (FL) ---------> Terminal M2
Motor Back-Left (BL) ---------> Terminal M3
Motor Back-Right (BR) ---------> Terminal M4

[ SERVOS (Weapon Systems) ]
---------------------------
Spike Servo (Rear) -------------> SER1 Port (Signal Pin 10)
Cannon Servo (Front) -----------> SER2 Port (Signal Pin 9)
* Servo Wiring: Brown (GND), Red (5V), Orange (Signal)

[ BLUETOOTH MODULE (HC-05/06) ]
-------------------------------
HC-05 VCC ----------------------> Arduino 5V
HC-05 GND ----------------------> Arduino GND
HC-05 TXD ----------------------> Arduino RX (Pin 0)
HC-05 RXD ----------------------> Arduino TX (Pin 1)
* Note: Disconnect RX/TX while uploading code.

[ ESP32-CAM (Video Feed & AI) ]
-------------------------------
ESP32-CAM 5V -------------------> External 5V / Battery VCC
ESP32-CAM GND ------------------> Common GND
ESP32-CAM TX (GPIO 1) ----------> Arduino Analog Pin A2 (SoftwareSerial RX)
* Note: Use 115200 Baud for IP check and 9600 for data communication.

================================================================================
      SYSTEM CONFIG: WHEEL DRIVE | SPIKE: SER1 | CANNON: SER2 | BAUD: 9600
================================================================================
